Name: Jamaica Barbecue Sauce
Ingredients: ['1 1/2 c. cider vinegar', '4 tsp. lemon juice', '3 tsp. Worcestershire sauce', '2 tsp. brown sugar', '1 Tbsp. prepared mustard', '3/4 tsp. salt', '1/2 tsp. meat tenderizer', '1 c. tomato catsup', '1 Tbsp. liquid smoke', '1 tsp. garlic powder', '1 tsp. cayenne pepper', '1/2 tomato puree']

Name: Catatini
Ingredients: ['1 pkg. pepperoni', '1 lb. ground meat', '1 jar spaghetti sauce', '1 pkg. shredded cheese', '1 pkg. elbow noodles', 'salt and pepper to taste']

Name: Cornish Game Hen (With Wild Rice)
Ingredients: ['2 Cornish game hens', '1 box chicken flavored wild rice (wild and white mixed or wild and brown mixed)', '1/2 c. raisins (optional)', 'some salt (for flavoring)']

Name: Smore Pie
Ingredients: ['1 graham cracker crust (9 oz.)', '12 oz. chocolate bar, broken in pieces', '6 oz. hot fudge (warm)', '30 regular marshmallows', '3/4 c. milk', '2 1/2 c. whipped cream (reserve 1 c. for topping)']

Name: Rich Pastry Crust
Ingredients: ['2 1/2 cups flour, all-purpose', '1 teaspoon salt', '1/2 cup lard', '1/4 cup schmaltz (chicken fat) cold', '6 tablespoons water']
